text: Lineynoye () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Lineyninsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 832 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 58 km from Astrakhan, 89 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Lineynoye
